casebody.data:
FRANCES ALINE BALDWIN v. WALTER J. BALDWIN, JR. 26 So. (2nd) 502

June Term, 1946

June 11, 1946 Division B Cushman & Woodard, for petitioner. Thomas H. Anderson, for respondent. PER CURIAM:

The petition for certiorari is granted and the order of the chancellor denying the motion to dismiss the bill of complaint is quashed. Chisholm v. Chisholm, 98 Fla. 1196, 125 So. 694; Pillard v. Pillard, 127 Fla. 682, 173 So. 838.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ„ concur.
